snippet.title: Lost Luggage for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Nice Kaboom! r.-o.

But damn, "Luggage" sounds so delicious and tasty...And that this word is "Gebäck" in German doesn't help either, as that word sounds like "Gebäck" which is cookies or biscuits translated into English. 

Damn words that sound like something to eat!!! DAMN THEM!!!
